label goodhorseending:
    scene black with llongdissolve
    "{size=*2}Will be continued...{/size}" with longdissolve
    scene wall with llongdissolve
    play music "audio/oddish00.ogg" fadein 3.0 volume 0.5
    t "Would you look at that!"
    show cat20smug with moveinleft
    t "You just finished the first part of this amazing journey."
    t "Got a kiss, got some meat to fill all your holes-"
    t "I'd say you just got the best ending for this route!"
    t "Well, the first part of the route at least, out of three!"
    t "Hmm, you do seem a little confused there."
    hide cat20smug
    show cat20
    t "Yup, in case you were wondering, this last route of the chapter is divided in three parts!"
    t "Each part focusing on the backstory of different very important individuals, whose lore will intertwine in a grandiose finale!"
    t "It sucks that we don't get to spend that much time together, but the little guy inside your head seems to get jealous enough already, so maybe it's for the best."
    t "So, what did you think so far?"
    hide cat20
    show cat20simple
    t "There are so many questions unanswered still...I know."
    t "I am still not entirely sure what to make of Therium, and I've known him for years!"
    hide cat20simple
    show cat20
    t "I'm sure we'll get more clear answers at some point, maybe in the next update, maybe the one after that, who knows?"
    t "Oh! Almost forgot!"
    t "One important piece of information I gotta tell you about the story!"
    t "You're probably used by now to veeeery long waiting time for HUGE updates with lots of content!"
    t "But for the next two parts of the route, expect more frequent, smaller updates."
    t "I wasn't given many more details, so...follow the author on Twitter, Patreon or Discord for more future information, I suppose."
    t "I gotta stop yappin'. Chelsie is holding a party tonight and I am invited, huehuehue!"
    hide cat20
    show cat20sadsmile
    t "You would've been too but Therium isn't a big party guy so...sorry."
    t "See ya in the next update, which should come faster than you'd expect, hopefully."
    hide cat20sadsmile
    show cat20
    t "Tate, out!"
    hide cat20 with moveoutleft
    scene black with llongdissolve
    jump credits

