label badhorseending:
    scene black with llongdissolve
    "{size=*2}Will be continued...{/size}" with longdissolve
    scene wall with llongdissolve
    play music "audio/triste.ogg" fadein 3.0 volume 0.8
    t "Would you look at that!"
    show cat20smug with moveinleft
    t "A perfect place to rest."
    hide cat20smug
    show cat20sadsmile
    t "Oh, hello there, are you new here?"
    t "Don't think I've seen you around before."
    t "Although you do look...familiar for some reason."
    t "Have we met before?"
    hide cat20sadsmile
    show cat20smug
    t "Heh, what am I saying? I would never forget a handsome face like yours."
    hide cat20smug
    show cat20smile
    t "Do you wanna sit here with me?"
    hide cat20smile
    show cat20simple
    t "I've been running around looking for someone...but I forgot who...and why."
    t "I'm pretty sure I came here with another purpose in mind as well, but I don't remember that either."
    t "Weird."
    t "I do have this sudden urge to say..."
    t "Roll the credits? Huh."
    scene black with llongdissolve
    t "And to...cry?"
    jump credits
